        </table>
      </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
      <td style="font-weight: normal;background-color: #FFFFFF;">You can also choose from 3 different rendering methods to show nesting, Grid (like most of this document), Bubbles and Lines (see the Edit -&gt; Layout Render Style menu). Together with horizontal/vertical, this gives 6 different styles:
